name: INTERCELLAR
description: InterCellar is an RWA marketplace focused on luxury wine and spirits, allowing collectors, enthusiasts and investors to acquire and trade premium bottles as real world assets. Every bottle purchased on the platform receives a digital twin minted on the blockchain, stored in the userâ€™s wallet while the physical asset is held in a secure facility. These digital twins can be traded or exchanged, bringing liquidity, traceability and transparency to a traditionally illiquid market. InterCellar merges fine wine expertise with blockchain infrastructure to offer a secure, authenticated and frictionless way to invest in rare wines and spirits.
